name: Noblen® AZ894E8-A Natural
description:
Noblen® AZ894E8-A Natural is a high performance polypropylene impact copolymer. It is used in automotive trim parts requiring superior impact, scratch, and scuff resistance. This product is suitable for Injection molding.

 

Applications:


Large components 
Appliances
Automotive Interior Trim
Boat
Jet-propelled Vehicle 


 

Features:


Excellent durability in high-traffic areas


 

Benefits:


High scratch, scuff, and mar resistance
